{"type": "article", "id": 29122, "title": "杂志架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T22:55:23Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 82, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607042027542ds5B78mMjtQFA6h.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>书籍和杂志往往被摆放在桌面或者书架上，<a href=\"http://www.alvarodiazhernandez.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Álvaro Díaz Hernández</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.nyova.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NYOVA</a> 设计了一款墙上杂志架 ON 提供了一种新的收纳选择，而且本身也可以作为一件简单漂亮的装饰物。ON 由四个木块和一条耐用的皮革绳组成，固定时只要用杂志夹住细绳让它自然地支撑在木块上即可。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.nyova.com/en/producto/on/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 209 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704205443Gc72041qTDiyBRVS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607042054430aPgChSjA26qMwFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704205443M8KgpUGm4Q2EoYIj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704205443zO8xUEeq9nHTNIw5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}